Use the Linux instructions if you re installing in Windows Subsystem for Clone the repo: git clone https: github.com postgresml postgresml Start Dockerized PostgresML will run on port , just in case you already have Postgres running: cd postgresml && up Connect to Postgres in the container with PostgresML installed: psql postgres: postgres@localhost:5433 pgml_development Validate your To ensure you get the most out of your SmartGrip experience, we have answered several of the most commonly asked questions and provided a few helpful tips How do I use SmartGrip? To use SmartGrip, simply attach it to any compatible golf glove (only ™ gloves by Titliest and FootJoy at this time) prior to each Once attached, it’ll blink three times to let you know it’s If it does not blink or turn on, try rotating the chip slightly while on the Next, make sure you are holding the golf club correctly by placing the grip of the club in the fingers of your lead hand (NOT the palm). It should feel like you are holding a hammer and there is plenty of wrist Lastly, rotate your lead hand clockwise until you see the green light turn on, indicating you are properly using a strong grip and you are ready to hit the SmartGrip was developed and engineered with some of the best PGA Tour players and professional to ensure you learn a proper strong power What do I do if my new SmartGrip chip doesn t seem to work or turn on? In some rare cases, the magnet in the gloves varies in strength causing some chips to need an adjustment to power To fix this, simply rotate or turn your SmartGrip chip until the green light blinks three It is now turned on, ready to go, and will work PLEASE NOTE: The chip might even seem like it is slightly hanging off the plastic casing on the glove, but we assure you the chip will not come off and will Also, SmartGrip was designed primarily to develop healthy grip habits for drives and to correct a Because of this, SmartGrip works best on longer clubs, such as drivers, woods, hybrids, and longer It feels really awkward to hold the golf club when using Is that normal? Yes, this is completely normal! After developing a habit with an incorrect grip over a long period of time, learning a proper grip will feel strange at Most people hold the golf club in the palm of their hands, which can severely limit control and Instead, hold the grip of the club in the fingers of your hand (like you would a hammer) . This will feel much more controllable and make SmartGrip feel more However, since the SmartGrip chip can be used outdoors and indoors, try giving a few practice swings before heading to the If you’re already at the course (go low!), the awkwardness will usually go away after a bucket of balls at the range or after the first few Is SmartGrip a golf glove? No, SmartGrip is not a It is a golf training aid designed to work seamlessly with any compatible golf glove from Titliest or You simply replace the ball marker that came with your glove with your SmartGrip What is a strong grip? And why should I use it? SmartGrip helps reinforce the use of what is commonly known in golf as a “strong” grip position, which has proven to dramatically help correct a majority of issues, including ball contact, slicing, distance, and Because the grip is such a core fundamental in golf , we decided to launch the Umbrella golf grip chip with this in mind, with other grip enhancements comin

It can often become a Today, we’re listing tips to enhance money communication and organization between you and your Read on to learn more about saving money as a Enjoy! Separate Accounts Separating your accounts is the best way to avoid any complicated financial situation and arguments related to Decide in the beginning of the relationship how you choose to manage personal In some cultures families, one partner is the main In others, it’s 50. Be sure to discuss and decide prior to settling Each of you can have one personal account then you can create a joint account for common Financial Transparency Financial transparency in a couple is important if you are to join money or make common For example to buy a house, You need to know their credit history, how they manage their accounts, do they have debt they must repay, do they sustain family members or children? What would you do if you suddenly discover they have more debt than expected? Financial complications are responsible of % of couples arguments . Just like you wouldn’t expect your partner to cheat, financial transparency should be the basis of a trustworthy Don’t Make Money a Taboo The best way to create lies and taboos in a relationship is to never mention certain subjects, or when you do, to always relate it to a negative Following the previous examples, if you suddenly discover that your partner is in debt, shouting at them won’t solve any Instead, sit down calmly with them to try to figure out how they got themselves in this situation in the first Next, try to figure out a viable solution to their While a partner is not a coach, financial advisor or therapist, patience and trust are Not everybody is comfortable with money management, and your partner may be one of these Therefore, taking the time to actually discuss it and not making it a taboo is essential for the wellbeing and future of the Become the household CFO If, after following the previous advice, you figure your spouse has issues managing money, you can always take charge of that aspect of the The Finnt App is specially designed for the main account user to keep track of various expenses and help their family members (sub account users) manage their money as efficiently as You can also set up savings accounts to help them achieve goals and teach them the power of compound Download Finnt Get started with Finnt Related posts: Managing Personal Finances Welcome Paula! User Segments - ValidMind Home Why ValidMind Use Cases Platform Overview About Request A Demo Model risk defense What is model risk defense? The process to define, develop, validate, and release a new model into production is often referred to as the model development life This life cycle is divided up in three areas of responsibilities or as it is referred to in the Financial Services industry - three lines of These responsibilities are divided between three organizational roles - line, line, and line of defense - that are tasked to manage a model s life cycle and Request A Demo For information about how ValidMind handles your personal data, please see our privacy policy . ValidMind Supports The Entire Model Risk Organization At ValidMind we are committed to supporting the entire Model Risk organization by providing them with modern tools, as well as superior service and For more information about our solution or if you have questions about how to best reach us, please visit How to Contact Us . Line OF DEFENSE For Model Developers The line of defense is the responsibility of the model business owner and the model This group defines the business requirements and translates them into model proposals, gathers, cleans, and formats data that will be used within the model, and develops and extensively tests the model to ensure it delivers the intended business use case They are also responsible for documenting any results, testing, and assumptions applied to the Documentation & Test Automation ValidMind is the single platform to collect, manage, and automate your model documentation and Freedom Of Choice With ValidMind developers choose their way of working and their preferred choice of Faster Deployment With ValidMind developers and validators can work in unison to ensure that the final approval process is a simple Line OF DEFENSE For Model Validator Teams The line of defense is the responsibility of the model risk management and validation This team assesses the model risk independent of the team that built the model (and thus created the risk exposure). The validation team reviews and evaluates the model and the model documentation to ensure it complies with commercial and regulatory requirements and that the model delivers on the intended business use case subject to regulatory The validation team must also challenge the assumptions made by the model developer before approving the model for production Centralized, Consolidated View ValidMind offers a consolidated view of all your model projects, communication with model developers and the model review Effective & Systematic Model Validation Our interactive dashboard helps you identify top model risks, collaborate to improve models, and increase model workflow Ease of Reporting ValidMind helps you create documentation templates for each model use This makes it easy to generate reproducible and documentation for every Line OF DEFENSE For Audit Teams The line of defense is the responsibility of internal and external auditors, as well as regulatory bodies (such as the Federal Reserve or FDIC in the US). these are systems that we are all very familiar with and are exceptionally good at doing ONE thing but nothing Think about a It can’t do anything other than drive it cannot write you a story or hold a conversation with Another example of an ANI system is Alexa or Siri, which you use to do simple tasks, but they cannot do anything (AGI) - these are systems that can do everything that you can do only these systems can do these tasks much faster, more accurately, and efficiently than any person could without the need to sleep, take a break, or a These AGI systems are the next evolution of AI that are not far off in the Rather they are already knocking on our respective These systems will mark a clear shift in how we work, earn, compete, and thrive as individuals, companies, and nations in the coming We believe that it is essential for every company, individual, and nation to have an AGI strategy, as it is most likely several years away and not several Quantum AI: One of the areas we are most interested in and excited about is the combination of quantum computing and artificial intelligence We believe that once combined, the computational power of quantum systems will lay the foundation for Artificial General Intelligence systems and other advancements in drug discovery, chemistry, climate, biotech, engineering, and We spend a significant portion of our time working with our partners in the quantum computing field to test new ideas, develop new projects, and support the advancement of quantum artificial If you are a student, researcher, startup, or company working in Quantum AI, we’d love to speak with ABOUT RESEARCH BUILD Contact CREATED BY HUMANS WITH AI, FOR HUMANS & CREATED BY HUMANS WITH AI, FOR HUMANS & [ EMERGENTAI ] EMERGENT LINE THE FOUNDER Made on Tilda   EmergentAI -
